ton and Tyson Gay fumbled the exchange heading into the last leg of the semifinal race, costing the U.S. a spot in the final.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Darvis_Patton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Darvis Patton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Darvis_Patton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Darvis_Patton\"}, {\"begin\": 940, \"end\": 949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyson_Gay\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tyson Gay\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyson_Gay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyson_Gay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2016, the United States finished in position for a bronze medal, but was disqualified after the exchange between Mike Rodgers and Justin Gatlin occurred outside of the designated zone.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1071, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999234039738033, \"rank\": 7.051441403088619e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Rodgers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mike Rodgers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Rodgers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Rodgers\"}, {\"begin\": 1191, \"end\": 1204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Gatlin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Justin Gatlin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Gatlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Gatlin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tokyo Olympics saw the United States fail to make it past its preliminary heat because of another bungled baton exchange, this time between Fred Kerley and Ronnie Baker.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1274, \"end\": 1287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999234039738033, \"rank\": 7.051441403088619e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fred Kerley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\"}, {\"begin\": 1407, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ronnie_Baker_(musician)\", \"score\": 0.8861489246657742, \"rank\": 0.12847818619032164, \"text\": \"Ronnie Baker\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ronnie_Baker_(musician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ronnie_Baker_(musician)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lewis later doubled down on his statement, expressing his issues with the system on X.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether the United States will listen to Lewis, who won gold in the 4x100-relay twice, is to be determined, but it's clear something needs to change before Los Angeles in 2028.\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1522, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999234039738033, \"rank\": 7.051441403088619e-05, \"text\": \"United St